These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, milk
There 3 different types of food: kale, pear, cucumber
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, writing, drawing
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, doctor, engineer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, jazz, punk
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, pakistani, australian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, badminton, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is the pakistani##1
 2. the person who's sport is surfing is the engineer##1
 3. the person drinking milk is between the australian and the person drinking water##2
 4. the fan of jazz is on the left of the spanish##1
 5. the doctor is the person eating cucumber##1
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is the spanish##1
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person eating kale##1
 8. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the doctor##1
10. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | water    | milk   | sprite           |
| Food          | pear       | cucumber    | kale         |
| Hobby         | writing    | drawing  | video-games        |
| Job           | pilot | doctor   | engineer      |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | punk    | reggae       |
| Nationality   | pakistani     | spanish  | australian       |
| Sport         | parkour     | badminton | surfing |

