.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, cola
There 3 different types of food: corn, apple, cabbage
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, fantasy, zombie
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, folk, indie
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, pakistani, egyptian
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, goldfish, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, surfing, climbing
 1. the owner of the rat is the pakistani##1
 2. the owner of the rat is the person watching zombie movies##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking 7up##2
 5. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking tea is the fan of hip-hop##1
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 8. the person eating corn is the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the fan of indie##1
10. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | 7up   | cola    | tea         |
| Food          | corn    | apple | cabbage          |
| Movie-Genre   | sports  | zombie  | fantasy     |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | folk      | hip-hop         |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | pakistani   | japanese    |
| Pet           | rabbit        | rat      | goldfish         |
| Sport         | surfing | tennis  | climbing |

