There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, brazilian, malaysian
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, lizard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, skiing, rugby
 1. the person eating potato is the owner of the goat##1
 2. the malaysian is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 3. the person watching western movies is the person eating onion##1
 4. the person watching musical movies is the owner of the goat##1
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the brazilian and the fan of funk##2
 8. the brazilian is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
 9. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person eating potato##1
11. the brazilian is the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
