The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, jazz, trance
3 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, parkour, climbing
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, trike, roller
 1. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is parkour and the fan of jazz##2
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is handball and the owner of the pony##2
 7. the person driving the helicopter is between the person eating avocado and the person drinking milk##2
 8. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 9. the firefighter is on the right of the fan of funk##1
10. the coach is the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | milk          | cola         | iced-tea      |
| Food          | artichoke     | zucchini         | avocado |
| Job           | entrepreneur | firefighter    | coach   |
