 3. the malaysian is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the malaysian##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
