.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, 7up
There 3 different types of food: pear, onion, strawberry
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, woodworking, reading
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, photographer, journalist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, colasy, time-travel
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, rowing
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, trike, quad-bike
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the journalist##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person eating onion is on the left of the scientist##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is between the person watching musical movies and the photographer##2
5. the person eating strawberry is between the journalist and the person who's hobby is reading##2
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
8. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person watching colasy movies is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | cola      | mirinda      | 7up       |
| Food          | onion      | strawberry    | pear   |
| Hobby         | reading    | camping     | woodworking     |
| Job           | photographer    | scientist | journalist   |
| Movie-Genre   | colasy    | time-travel    | musical       |
| Sport         | rowing | golf      | ice-hockey    |
| Transport     | trike       | bike | quad-bike |

