.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, tea, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: avocado, radish, corn
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, writing, sudoku
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, disaster, iced-teasy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, hip-hop, funk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, sailing, soccer
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, helicopter
1. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person watching iced-teasy movies is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person eating radish is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
6. the person eating corn is on the right of the fan of funk##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
8. the person driving the car is the person watching iced-teasy movies##1
9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | lemonade     | tea         |
| Food          | avocado     | radish      | corn     |
| Hobby         | writing | sudoku    | skydiving      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller   | disaster | iced-teasy    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop        | funk     | techno   |
| Sport         | rugby     | sailing | soccer |
| Transport     | train     | helicopter       | car    |

