.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, juice
There 3 different types of food: banana, pepper, onion
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, journalist, teacher
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, thai, colombian
3 different pets are kept: lizard, fish, hamster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, skateboarding, water-polo
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, motorbike
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating onion##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the analyst is between the person drinking juice and the owner of the hamster##2
4. the mexican is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
7. the journalist is the person eating banana##1
8. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
9. the thai is between the person eating banana and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | lemonade    | hot-chocolate       | juice      |
| Food          | banana   | onion   | pepper  |
| Job           | journalist  | analyst | teacher    |
| Nationality   | mexican   | thai     | colombian  |
| Pet           | hamster     | lizard        | fish |
| Sport         | skateboarding | badminton   | water-polo  |
| Transport     | quad-bike    | motorbike     | scooter      |

 